hasn't stamped my two articles.

547
00:34:55,226 --> 00:34:55,787
Why?

548
00:34:56,586 --> 00:34:57,787
Any problem with the facts?

549
00:34:59,347 --> 00:35:01,467
Editor Xiao, I swear by my profession

550
00:35:01,506 --> 00:35:02,626
that in my two articles,

551
00:35:02,626 --> 00:35:04,066
every word written is true.

552
00:35:05,586 --> 00:35:07,307
Since there's no problem with the facts,

553
00:35:07,546 --> 00:35:08,747
why haven't they stamped it?

554
00:35:09,146 --> 00:35:10,787
They don't deny the details.

555
00:35:11,467 --> 00:35:13,867
They deny the entire fact itself.

556
00:35:15,347 --> 00:35:16,867
This is simply absurd.

557
00:35:17,666 --> 00:35:20,387
How can they deny something
that actually happened?

558
00:35:26,787 --> 00:35:27,307
Wait.

559
00:35:28,626 --> 00:35:30,947
Isn't your girlfriend
the mayor of Yuehai Town?

560
00:35:32,146 --> 00:35:33,267
Even she denies it?

561
00:35:44,987 --> 00:35:45,487
Mr. Du,

562
00:35:46,747 --> 00:35:47,467
