563
00:35:49,186 --> 00:35:49,706
Proof?

564
00:35:51,907 --> 00:35:53,226
Yes, I do.

565
00:35:55,546 --> 00:35:57,747
Editor Xiao,
here's my interview summary.

566
00:35:58,506 --> 00:36:00,787
Every piece of material in my article

567
00:36:00,787 --> 00:36:02,626
