I paid in Yuehai.

571
00:36:09,666 --> 00:36:11,226
And this is my land use certificate.

572
00:36:13,106 --> 00:36:14,427
City construction fee?

573
00:36:16,867 --> 00:36:17,467
Editor Xiao,

574
00:36:17,907 --> 00:36:20,186
I can guarantee
that in these two articles,

575
00:36:20,186 --> 00:36:21,506
everything written is solid fact.

576
00:36:21,787 --> 00:36:23,546
They're common knowledge
throughout Yuehai

577
00:36:23,586 --> 00:36:25,427
against any investigation
and verification.

578
00:36:26,827 --> 00:36:27,347
I understand.

579
00:36:28,307 --> 00:36:29,987
If the content is accurate,

580
00:36:30,506 --> 00:36:33,066
we don't necessarily need
their approval to print the articles.

581
00:36:35,347 --> 00:36:36,706
I'll handle this matter.

582
00:36:39,626 --> 00:36:41,006
Mr. Qian, look.

583
00:36:41,467 --> 00:36:44,347
With one command,
it prints ten thousand copies per hour.

584
00:36:44,867 --> 00:36:46,106
The speed is incredibly fast.

585
00:36:50,626 --> 00:36:51,747
Not only is it fast,

586
00:36:52,026 --> 00:36:54,827
but it also uses half the electricity
of other printers.

587
00:36:56,506 --> 00:36:57,066
Not bad.

588
00:36:58,427 --> 00:36:59,226
(Printing Pioneer)
Not bad at all.

589
00:36:59,827 --> 00:37:02,347
Here, sir, have a smoke.

590
00:37:04,226 --> 00:37:05,146
Forgot where we are.

591
00:37:05,706 --> 00:37:06,747
Let's smoke outside.

592
00:37:07,427 --> 00:37:07,927
Thank you.

593
00:37:08,226 --> 00:37:08,826
How about this?

594
00:37:09,146 --> 00:37:11,827
Give me a set

595
00:37:12,106 --> 00:37:14,747
of the pictures and information
of this printer.

596
00:37:14,787 --> 00:37:15,287
I'll take it

597
00:37:15,467 --> 00:37:17,787
to show the printery owners.

598
00:37:17,987 --> 00:37:18,626
No problem.

599
00:37:26,787 --> 00:37:27,307
Good.

600
00:37:28,747 --> 00:37:30,467
It's truly...

601
00:37:30,866 --> 00:37:33,490
(New City Life)

602
00:37:35,922 --> 00:37:40,498
(Yuehai Column: Seven-Up or Eight-Down?
No Land Sales. What's Next for Yuehai?)

603
00:37:45,387 --> 00:37:45,947
Du,

604
00:37:46,987 --> 00:37:47,827
