659
00:41:07,947 --> 00:41:08,987
Mr. Zhao, I'm sorry.

660
00:41:09,267 --> 00:41:11,387
I have a very important matter
to report to you.

661
00:41:13,747 --> 00:41:14,247
Wang.

662
00:41:14,666 --> 00:41:15,166
- Come.
- Coming.

663
00:41:16,546 --> 00:41:18,106
Mr. Zhao, everyone's here.

664
00:41:18,347 --> 00:41:19,226
Take this inside.

665
00:41:19,347 --> 00:41:19,847
Okay.

666
00:41:19,867 --> 00:41:22,046
Then I'll give you five minutes.
Go ahead.

667
00:41:45,867 --> 00:41:49,427
Didn't Yuehai Column previously publish
some articles that got a great response?

668
00:41:49,867 --> 00:41:50,367
Yes.

669
00:41:50,907 --> 00:41:53,106
The situation
is truly different this time.

670
00:41:53,666 --> 00:41:55,467
Yuehai hasn't fully developed yet.

671
00:41:55,626 --> 00:41:58,347
All our measures
are exploratory and experimental.

672
00:41:58,506 --> 00:41:59,907
If this kind of controversial issue

673
00:42:00,146 --> 00:42:01,546
spreads far and wide,

674
00:42:01,747 --> 00:42:03,307
