682
00:42:18,747 --> 00:42:20,827
If you report it up
through the chain of command,

683
00:42:21,146 --> 00:42:22,347
I'm afraid time will run out.

684
00:42:22,807 --> 00:42:24,666
And it's a provincial capital newspaper.

685
00:42:24,827 --> 00:42:26,387
We don't want to cause you trouble.

686
00:42:26,787 --> 00:42:29,186
So we want to report directly
to the provincial level.

687
00:42:30,706 --> 00:42:32,407
I... I understand.

688
00:42:32,706 --> 00:42:34,867
You're not here
to ask for my permission.

689
00:42:34,947 --> 00:42:35,907
You came to inform me.

690
00:42:36,146 --> 00:42:37,307
Worried about overstepping?

691
00:42:38,307 --> 00:42:39,787
Li, you've really improved now.

692
00:42:40,267 --> 00:42:41,907
You consider problems very thoroughly.

693
00:42:42,867 --> 00:42:43,947
The plan you mentioned

694
00:42:43,947 --> 00:42:46,186
is indeed the most effective solution
right now.

695
00:42:46,546 --> 00:42:47,226
Yes, Mr. Zhao.

696
00:42:47,787 --> 00:42:48,586
We also don't know

697
00:42:48,586 --> 00:42:51,146
what the outcome will be
after reporting upwards.

698
00:42:51,987 --> 00:42:52,747
I understand.

699
00:42:53,706 --> 00:42:55,586
Since you've made up
your minds to do this,

700
00:42:55,586 --> 00:42:56,467
then I agree.

701
00:42:57,827 --> 00:42:59,307
It's fine. But rest assured.

702
00:42:59,747 --> 00:43:01,787
No matter the outcome,
I will take responsibility.

